@startuml microsoft_azure-realtime-fraud-detection

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<event>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<processing>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<storage>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<compute>> LightPink
}

component "Event Generator" as EventGen
component "Azure Event Hub" as EventHub <<event>>
component "Azure Stream Analytics" as StreamAnalytics <<processing>>
component "Azure Machine Learning" as AzureML <<compute>>
component "Azure Functions" as Functions <<compute>>
component "Azure Synapse Analytics" as Synapse <<storage>>
component "Azure Cosmos DB" as CosmosDB <<storage>>

EventGen -right-> EventHub : Generate events
EventHub -right-> StreamAnalytics : Ingest events
StreamAnalytics -down-> Synapse : Persist data
StreamAnalytics -down-> CosmosDB : Persist data
StreamAnalytics -right-> Functions : Trigger analysis
AzureML -up-> Functions : Provide ML model
Functions -down-> CosmosDB : Query/Update data

note top of EventHub : Real-time transaction ingestion
note bottom of StreamAnalytics : Real-time analysis
note right of AzureML : Model training & deployment
note left of Functions : Orchestration & fraud detection
note bottom of Synapse : Historical analysis
note bottom of CosmosDB : SQL & Gremlin APIs

@enduml